#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&palapeli; is a single-player jigsaw puzzle game. With it you can create and "
"play puzzles ranging from 4 to 10,000 pieces. This version includes "
"facilities to assist in solving large puzzles (300 pieces or more) within "
"the size limits of a computer screen."
msgstr ""
"&palapeli; je igra jigsaw slagalica. Sa njom možete kreirati i igrati "
"slagalice, u rasponu od 4 do 10 000 dijelova. Ova verzija uključuje i opcije "
"kako bi pomogli u rješavanju velikih slagalice (300 dijelova i više) unutar "
"ograničene veličine kompjuterskog ekrana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main &palapeli; window is separated into two areas, the puzzle "
"collection and the puzzle table."
msgstr ""
"Glavni &palapeli; prozor je podijeljen u dva područja, prikupljanje "
"slagalice i tabela slagalice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid "This manual continues by describing those two areas."
msgstr "Ovaj priručnik nastavlja opisujući ta dva područja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing the puzzle collection"
msgstr "Pregledavanje kolekcije slagalica"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing puzzles and updating the collection"
msgstr "Igranje slagalice i ažuriranje kolekcije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you launch &palapeli; for the first time, your puzzle collection "
"already contains some sample puzzles that come with &palapeli;. Click on one "
"of them to start playing immediately. Later, when you have created some of "
"your own puzzles (see below), you can also click on them to start playing."
msgstr ""
"Kada pokrenete &palapeli; prvi put, tvoja kolekcija slagalica već sadrži "
"neke primjere slagalica koje dolaze s  palapeli;. Kliknite na jednu od njih "
"da početnete igrati odmah. Kasnije, kada ste kreirali neke od svojih "
"vlastitih slagalica (vidi ispod), također možete kliknuti na njih za početak "
"igre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Play takes place on the puzzle table; see <link linkend=\"puzzletable\">the "
"section after next</link> for how to use the puzzle table."
msgstr ""
"Igra se odvija na puzzle tabeli;  Za kako koristiti puzzle tabelu, "
"pogledajte <link linkend=\"puzzletable\">the section after next</link> ."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can select and highlight puzzles in the puzzle list by pressing "
#| "&Ctrl; and &LMB; together. Pressing the &LMB; or &RMB; without &Ctrl; "
#| "opens that puzzle for playing in the puzzle table."
msgid ""
"You can select and highlight puzzles in the puzzle list by hold the &Ctrl; "
"key and click with the &LMB;. Pressing the &LMB; or &RMB; without the &Ctrl; "
"key opens that puzzle for playing in the puzzle table."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati i istaknuti slagalice na listi slagalica pritiskom &Ctrl; i "
"&LMB; zajedno. Pritiskom na &LMB; ili &RMB; bez &Ctrl; otvara se ta "
"slagalica za igranje u tabeli slagalice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "On Apple OS X you need to double-click the &LMB; to begin playing. A "
#| "single click will just select and highlight one entry in the puzzle list."
msgid ""
"On &macOS; you need to double-click with the &LMB; to begin playing. A "
"single click will just select and highlight one entry in the puzzle list."
msgstr ""
"Na Apple OS x potrebno je dva puta kliknuti &LMB; za početak igrice. Jednim "
"klikom ćete samo selektovati i označiti jedan unos u puzzle listu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As well as playing a puzzle, you can use the puzzle collection for the "
"following actions:"
msgstr ""
"Kao i za igranje slagalice, možete koristiti kolekciju slagalica za sljedeće "
"akcije:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>create</emphasis> new puzzles from images on your disk"
msgstr "<emphasis>create</emphasis> nove slagalice sa slike na tvoj disk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>import</emphasis> puzzles made by others"
msgstr "<emphasis>import</emphasis> puzzles napravljene od strane drugih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>export</emphasis> puzzles to share them with your friends and the "
"world"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>export</emphasis> puzzles kako bi ih podijelili sa svojim "
"prijateljima i svijetu"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>delete</emphasis> puzzles you do not need any more"
msgstr "<emphasis>delete</emphasis> puzzles ne trebate više"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The following section shows how to perform these tasks with the toolbar "
#| "buttons."
msgid ""
"The following section shows how to perform these tasks with the action icons "
"in the toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Sljedeće poglavlje pokazuje kako obavljati ove poslove s dugmadima sa alatne "
"trake."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80 index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar overview"
msgstr "Pregled alatne trake"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:83
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Create new puzzle"
msgid "Create New Puzzle…"
msgstr "Nova slagalica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens a dialog which allows you to create a puzzle from an image on "
"your disk.</action> See <link linkend=\"create-puzzles\">the next chapter</"
"link> for details."
msgstr ""
"<action> Otvara dijaloški okvir koji vam omogućuva kreiranje slagalice sa "
"slike na vašem disku. </action> Pogledajte <link linkend=\"create-puzzles"
"\">the next chapter</link>  za detalje."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:89
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Delete puzzle"
msgid "Delete Puzzle"
msgstr "Izbrisati slagalicu"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:90 index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Any puzzles that you have selected in the puzzle list, will be permanently "
"deleted from your collection."
msgstr ""
"Bilo koja slagalica koju ste odabrali u listi slagalica, bit će trajno "
"izbrisana iz vaše kolekcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90 index.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid "This action cannot be undone."
msgstr "Ova akcija ne može biti poništena."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:93
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Import from file"
msgid "Import from File…"
msgstr "Uvezi iz datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94 index.docbook:716
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<action>When you have received a &palapeli; puzzle file (which can "
#| "usually be recognized by the file extension <literal role=\"extension\">*."
#| "puzzle</literal>), you can use this action to import it into your local "
#| "collection.</action> Puzzle files can also be played by simply clicking "
#| "on them in the file manager of your choice, but after the import, the "
#| "puzzle will appear in your local collection, and you can safely delete "
#| "the downloaded puzzle file."
msgid ""
"<action>When you have received a &palapeli; puzzle file (which can usually "
"be recognized by the file extension <literal role=\"extension\">.puzzle</"
"literal>), you can use this action to import it into your local collection.</"
"action> Puzzle files can also be played by simply clicking on them in the "
"file manager of your choice, but after the import, the puzzle will appear in "
"your local collection, and you can safely delete the downloaded puzzle file."
msgstr ""
"<action> Kad ste primili &palapeli; datoteku slagalice (koji se obično mogu "
"prepoznati po nastavk uz datoteke <literal role=\"extension\">*.puzzle</"
"literal>), možete koristiti ovu akciju kako bi je uvesti u lokalnu "
"kolekciju. </action> Datoteke slagalice također se mogu igradi jednostavnim "
"klikom na njih u upravitelju datoteka po svom izboru, ali nakon uvoza, "
"slagalica će se pojaviti u vašoj lokalnoj kolekciji, a možete sigurno "
"izbrisati preuzetu datoteku slagalice."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:97
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Export to file"
msgid "Export to File…"
msgstr "Izvoz u datoteku"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:98 index.docbook:720
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will export the currently selected puzzles to files, in order to enable "
"you to give them to your friends, publish them on the web, or make backup "
"copies of your collection."
msgstr ""
"To će izvesti trenutno odabranu slagalicu iz datoteke, kako bi vam omogućili "
"da ih date svojim prijateljima, objavite na webu, ili napraviti rezervne "
"kopije vaše kolekcije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating new puzzles"
msgstr "Kreiraj novu slagalicu"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "The puzzle creation dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog za kreiranje slagalice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As described in <link linkend=\"toolbar-collection\">the previous "
#| "section</link>, you can create new puzzles by clicking on the "
#| "<guiicon>Create new puzzle</guiicon> button in the puzzle collection "
#| "window."
msgid ""
"As described in <link linkend=\"toolbar-collection\">the previous section</"
"link>, you can create new puzzles by clicking on the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"tools-wizard.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Create New "
"Puzzle…</guiicon> action icon in the puzzle collection window."
msgstr ""
"Kao što je opisano u <link linkend=\"toolbar-collection\">the previous "
"section</link>, možete stvoriti nove slagalice klikom na <guiicon> Kreiraj "
"novu slagalicu </guiicon> dugme u prozoru za kolekciju slagalice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Clicking this button opens the puzzle creation dialog, which consists of "
#| "three pages:"
msgid ""
"Clicking this action icon opens the puzzle creation dialog, which consists "
"of three pages:"
msgstr ""
"Klikom na ovo dugme otvara se dijalog za kreiranje slagalice, koji se "
"sastoji od tri stranice:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the first page, select an image file which will be sliced into pieces. Be "
"sure to enter the correct metadata for the image: You should give "
"attribution to the author of the image (&eg; the photographer or the "
"painter); please respect the copyright of the image author."
msgstr ""
"Na prvoj stranici, odaberite datoteku slike koja će biti izrezana na "
"komadiće. Budite sigurni da ste unijeli ispravne metapodatake za sliku: "
"trebali bi dati pripisivanje autoru slike (&eg;  fotograf ili slikar); "
"molimo poštujte autorska prava autora slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the second page, you can select the type of pieces into which the image "
"will be sliced. &palapeli; comes with a collection of slicers preinstalled, "
"but third-party slicers may also be available."
msgstr ""
"Na drugoj strani, možete selektovati tip dijela u koji će slika biti "
"izrezana. &palapeli; dolazi sa kolekcijom unaprijed instaliranih rezača, ali "
"treća-strana rezača takođe može biti na raspolaganju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the final page of the dialog, the selected slicer can be customized &eg; "
"by choosing a different piece count or by adjusting parameters of the piece "
"shape. The available set of options depends which slicer has been selected."
msgstr ""
"Na posljednjoj stranici dijaloga, rezač može biti prilagođen &npr; odabirom "
"različitog broja dijelova ili podešavanjem parametara oblika dijela. "
"Dostupni set opcija ovisi koji rezač je izabran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This manual will continue to discuss the slicers which come with &palapeli;. "
"If you have downloaded a third-party slicer plugin for &palapeli;, please "
"refer to the documentation of this plugin if you have trouble installing or "
"using it on your system."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj priručnik će nastaviti raspravljati o rezačima koje dolaze s "
"&palapeli;. Ako ste preuzeli treću-stranu dodatka rezača &palapeli;, molim "
"vas potražite u dokumentaciji ovog dodatka ako imate problema s "
"instaliranjem ili korištenjem na vašem sistemu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple slicers"
msgstr "Jednostavi rezači"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&palapeli; has two simple slicers, <quote>Classic jigsaw pieces</quote> "
#| "and <quote>Rectangular pieces</quote>. These slicers create simple "
#| "rectangular pieces either with or without connecting plugs."
msgid ""
"&palapeli; has two simple slicers, <guilabel>Classic jigsaw pieces</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Rectangular pieces</guilabel>. These slicers create "
"simple rectangular pieces either with or without connecting plugs."
msgstr ""
"&palapeli; imaju dva jednostavna rezača. <quote>Classic jigsaw pieces</"
"quote> i <quote>Rectangular pieces</quote>. Ovi rezači kreiranju jednostavne "
"pravougaone dijelove sa ili bez priključaka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Both slicers allow the piece count and the aspect ratio to be adjusted. "
#| "Dragging the aspect ratio slider to the left results in tall pieces, "
#| "adjusting it to the right produces wide pieces. The default selection "
#| "produces approximately square pieces."
msgid ""
"Both slicers allow the piece count and the aspect ratio to be adjusted. "
"Dragging the <guilabel>Piece aspect ratio:</guilabel> slider to the left "
"results in tall pieces, adjusting it to the right produces wide pieces. The "
"default selection produces approximately square pieces."
msgstr ""
"Oba rezača omogućavaju računati komade i omjer koji će biti prilagođen. "
"Povlačenje omjer klizača ulijevo rezultira visokim komadima, prilagođavajući "
"desnim širim komadima. Zadana selekcija proizvodi oko kvadratni komada."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "The advanced &i18n-psc;"
msgstr "Napredni  &i18n-psc;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &i18n-psc; produces realistic jigsaw pieces with various basic patterns:"
msgstr ""
"&i18n-PSC; proizvodi realne jigsaw dijelove s različitim osnovnim obrascima:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rectangular grid"
msgstr "Kvadratna mreža"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contains the well-known rectangular pieces."
msgstr "Sadrži  dobro poznate kvadratne dijelove."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cairo grid"
msgstr "Kairo mreža"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With its pentagonal pieces and unequal edge angles, it's rather hard to "
"puzzle because the pieces fit together in an unfamiliar manner."
msgstr ""
"Sa svojim peterokutnim dijelovima i nejednakim ivicama ugla, vrloje teško "
"slagati jer dijelovi stanu zajedno u nepoznatom način."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hexagonal grid"
msgstr "Šestougaona mreža"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "Produces hexagonal pieces, arranged like honeycomb cells."
msgstr ""
"Proizvodi šestougaonih dijelova, raspoređeni su kao u obliku ćelija saća."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotrex grid"
msgstr "Rotrex mreža"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Through a special composition of triangular, hexagonal and rectangular "
"pieces, the pieces form a pattern resembling to many intersecting circles."
msgstr ""
"Kroz poseban trougaoni sastav, šestougaoni i četverougaoni dijelovi, "
"dijelovi formiraju obrazac nalik mnogim krugovima koji se sijeku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Irregular grid"
msgstr "Nepravilna mreža"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This grid is available only if you have installed <application>qvoronoi</"
#| "application> from the <ulink url=\"http://www.qhull.org"
#| "\"><application>qhull</application> package</ulink>. "
#| "<application>qvoronoi</application> is used to calculate irregular piece "
#| "shapes from randomly placed points."
msgid ""
"This grid is available only if you have installed <application>qvoronoi</"
"application> from the <ulink url=\"https://www.qhull.org"
"\"><application>qhull</application> package</ulink>. <application>qvoronoi</"
"application> is used to calculate irregular piece shapes from randomly "
"placed points."
msgstr ""
"Ova mreža je dostupna samo ako ste instalirali <application> qvoronoi </"
"application> from the <ulink url = \"http://www.qhull.org\"> <application> "
"qhull </application> package </ulink>. <application> qvoronoi </application> "
"se koriste za proračun nepravilnog oblika komada iz nasumično postavljenih "
"poena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &i18n-psc; has various parameters which control the appearance of the "
"piece edges, especially the plugs on them. Default settings are provided for "
"all of these parameters. An additional preset mode is available which "
"reduces the amount of parameters to a bare minimum. The following parameters "
"are available usually:"
msgstr ""
" &i18n-psc;  ima raznih parametara koji određuju izgled ivica komada, "
"posebno utikač na njih. Zadane postavke su osigurane za sve ove parametre. "
"Dodatno podešeni način rada je dostupan koja smanjuje količinu parametara na "
"minimum. Sljedeći parametri su dostupni kao i obično:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:150
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Approx. piece count"
msgid "Piece count:"
msgstr "Približan broj dijelova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here set the exact number in which the image will sliced into pieces. This "
"option only appear if the mathematical logic of the slicer selected allows "
"any number."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:154
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Approx. piece count"
msgid "Approx. piece count:"
msgstr "Približan broj dijelova"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here set the desired number in which the image will sliced into pieces. This "
"option only appears if the mathematical logic of the selected slicer can "
"readjust this number."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:158
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Flipped edge percentage"
msgid "Flipped edge percentage:"
msgstr "Izvrnut procenat ivica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The probability for each plug to be flipped. A plug is considered flipped if "
"it points in the opposite direction as it would in a fully regular grid. On "
"the rectangular grid, this results in pieces with 3 or 4 plugs pointing "
"inwards resp. outwards. Position the slider at the very left to obtain the "
"normal fully regular grid. In the middle, plug orientation is random. At the "
"right, the grid is fully regular again, but with an <quote>alternate</quote> "
"rule. This does <emphasis>not</emphasis> mean reversal of all plugs: In the "
"alternate regular grid, for instance, each piece has four inward-pointing or "
"four outward-pointing plugs. This setting has no effect in the irregular "
"grid."
msgstr ""
"Vjerovatnost da se postiglo svako uklapanje. Izbočina se smatra uklopljenom "
"ako su bodovi u suprotnom redoslijedu nego što bi bili  u punoj redovnoj "
"mreži. Na kvadratnoj mreži, to rezultira u komade sa 3 ili 4 utikača "
"pokazujući prema unutra odnosno, prema vani. Postavite klizač skroz lijevo "
"da se dobije normalna potpuna  regularna mreža. U sredini, priključite "
"orijentacija izbočine je slučajno odabrana. Na desnoj strani, mreža je "
"ponovo potpuna regularna, ali sa <quote> alternate </quote> pravilom. Ovo  "
"<emphasis> not</emphasis> znači ukidanje svih izbočina: U alternativnoj "
"regularnoj mreži, na primjer, svaki komad ima četiri unutrašnja pokazivača "
"ili četiri vanjska pokazivač izbočina. Ova postavka nema efekta u "
"neregularnoj mreži."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:162
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Edge curviness"
msgid "Edge curviness:"
msgstr "Zakrivljenost ivica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Determines how curvy the edges are, &ie; how strongly the borders dent in or "
"bulge out. Move the slider to the very left to obtain straight edge lines "
"(except for the plugs)."
msgstr ""
"Određuje koliko su ivice zakrivljene, &tj; koliko snažno su okviri udubljeni "
"ili ispupčeni. Pomaknite klizač skroz lijevo da biste dobili ravnu ivicu "
"linije (osim za izbočine)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:166
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Plug size"
msgid "Plug size:"
msgstr "Veličina izbočine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Determines the size of the plug part of each edge. The default setting "
"(middle position of the slider) is chosen to look like a real puzzle. The "
"slider ranges from 50% to 150% this size, which already looks obscenely "
"large. The program tries very hard to avoid collisions between plugs. "
"Colliding edges are reshaped multiple times and shrinked in small steps. "
"However there still remain cases where no solution can be found, especially "
"for large plug sizes."
msgstr ""
"Određuje veličinu dijela izbočine za svaku ivicu. Zadata postavka (srednji "
"položaj klizača) je izabrana da izgleda kao prava slagalica. Klizač se kreće "
"od 50% do 150% ove veličine, koja već izgleda opsceno velika. Program vrlo "
"teško pokušava da izbjegne koliziju između izbočina. Podudarane ivice su "
"preoblikovane više puta i skupljene u malim koracima. Međutim, postoje "
"idalje slučajevi u kojima se može naći rješenje, posebno za velike veličine "
"izbočine."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:170
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Diversity of curviness"
msgid "Diversity of curviness:"
msgstr "Raznovrsnost zakrivljenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Determines how much the curviness (see above) varies between edges. Move "
#| "the slider to the left to make the dents and bulges look all the same. At "
#| "the right, there may occur very curvy and very straight borders."
msgid ""
"Determines how much the curviness (see above) varies between edges. Move the "
"slider to the left to make the dents and bulges look all the same. Position "
"the slider at the right, there may occur very curvy and very straight "
"borders."
msgstr ""
"Određuje koliko zakrivljenost (vidi gore) varira između ivica. Pomaknite "
"klizač ulijevo da bi udubljenja i ispupčenja izgledala isto. Zapravo, može "
"doći do vrlo zakrivljenog i vrlo ravnog okvira."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:174
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Diversity of plug position"
msgid "Diversity of plug position:"
msgstr "Raznovrsnost pozicija ispupčenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:175
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Determines how much the position of the plug on the edge varies. At the "
#| "very left, plugs are affixed to the middle of their edge."
msgid ""
"Determines how much the position of the plug on the edge varies. Position "
"the slider at the very left, plugs are affixed to the middle of their edge."
msgstr ""
"Određuje koliko varira položaj izbočine na ivici. Na samoj lijevoj strani, "
"izbočine su pričvršćene na sredini njihove ivice."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:178
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Diversity of plugs"
msgid "Diversity of plugs:"
msgstr "Raznovrsnost ispupčenja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:179
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Determines how individual the plugs look like. At the very left, plugs "
#| "look all the same. At the very right, each plug will be a unique piece of "
#| "art crafted especially for you."
msgid ""
"Determines how individual the plugs look like. Position the slider at the "
"very left, plugs look all the same. At the very right, each plug will be a "
"unique piece of art crafted especially for you."
msgstr ""
"Određuje kako pojedinačne izbočine izgledaju. Na samoj lijevoj strani, "
"izbočine izgledaju sve isto. Na samoj desni strani, svaka izbočina će biti "
"jedinstveni dio umjetnosti izrađen posebno za vas."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:182
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Irr.: Diversity of piece size"
msgid "Diversity of piece size:"
msgstr "Irr .: Raznovrsnost veličine komada"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only for irregular grid: Determines how the piece size varies. A very small "
"setting means nearly no variation; crystallite-like structure arise. Higher "
"settings produce very small and very large pieces."
msgstr ""
"Samo za nepravilnu mrežu: Određuje kako veličine komada variraju. Vrlo mali "
"postavka znači gotovo bez promjena;kirstalno nalik nastajanju strukture . "
"Više postavke proizvode vrlo male i vrlo velike komade."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:186
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Dump grid image"
msgid "Dump grid image:"
msgstr "Izdvoji sliku rešetke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save an image of the grid (black edges on white background) at <filename>~/"
"goldberg-slicer-dump.png</filename>. If a previous dump exists, it is "
"overwritten."
msgstr ""
"Sačuvajte sliku mreže (crne ivice na bijeloj pozadini) na <filename>~/"
"goldberg-slicer-dump.png</filename>. Ako postoji prethodno izvođenje, ono je "
"prepisano."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing on the puzzle table"
msgstr "Igranje na tablici slagalice"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Basic moves"
msgstr "Osnovni pokreti"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "The puzzle table (detail)"
msgstr "Tabela slagalice (detalj)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:202
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The object of the game is to assemble the given pieces into an image."
msgid "The goal of the game is to assemble the given pieces into an image."
msgstr "Cilj igre je sastaviti date komade u sliku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The floating Preview window shows you what that image should be. Use a "
#| "toolbar or menu action to show or hide the window. For a detailed "
#| "description, see <link linkend=\"puzzletable-preview\">The Preview "
#| "window</link>."
msgid ""
"The floating Preview window shows you what that image should be. Use a "
"toolbar or menu item to show or hide the window. For a detailed description, "
"see <link linkend=\"puzzletable-preview\">The Preview window</link>."
msgstr ""
"Plutajući prozor Preview vam pokazuje kako bi trebala izgledati ta slika. "
"Koristite alatnu traku ili menu akcije za prikazivanje ili sakrivanje "
"prozora. Za detaljan opis, pogledajte <link linkend=\"puzzletable-preview"
"\">The Preview window</link>.."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish to attempt a puzzle that has 300 or more pieces, please read the "
"chapter on <link linkend=\"large-puzzles\">Facilities for solving large "
"puzzles</link>, after you have read this chapter."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da pokušate slagalicu sa 300 ili više komada, pročitajte "
"poglavlje o <link linkend=\"large-puzzles\">Facilities for solving large "
"puzzles</link>, nakon što ste pročitali ovo poglavlje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can move a single piece by clicking and dragging it with the &LMB;. That "
"will leave the piece selected and highlighted. To move several pieces at "
"once, first select and highlight them, then click and drag just one of the "
"pieces. The rest will follow."
msgstr ""
"Možete premjestiti pojedinačni komad klikom i povlačenjem ga sa &LMB;. To će "
"ostaviti komad izabranim i istaknutim. Da biste premjestili nekoliko komada "
"odjednom, prvo odaberite i označite ih, a zatim kliknite i povucite samo "
"jedan od komada. Ostatak će pratiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:206
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can select and highlight multiple pieces by holding &Ctrl; and "
#| "clicking on them, or by dragging a rubberband around them with the &LMB;. "
#| "You can also use &Ctrl; and &LMB; to increase or decrease the current "
#| "selection one piece at a time."
msgid ""
"You can select and highlight multiple pieces by holding &Ctrl; and clicking "
"on them, or by dragging a rubberband around them with the &LMB;. You can "
"also hold the &Ctrl; key and click with the &LMB; to increase or decrease "
"the current selection one piece at a time."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati i naglasiti više komada držanjem &Ctrl; i klikom na njih, "
"ili povlačenjem Rubberband oko njih sa &LMB;. Također možete koristiti "
"&Ctrl; i &LMB; povećati ili smanjiti trenutni izbor jednog komada odjednom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To remove selection and highlighting, just click on an empty spot on the "
"puzzle table or on a piece that is not already selected."
msgstr ""
"Da biste uklonili izbor i naglašavanje, samo kliknite na prazno mesto na "
"tabeli slagalice ili na komad koji nije već odabran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you put one piece near a neighboring piece, both pieces will "
"automatically snap together and become joined (1). After pieces have been "
"snapped together, they cannot be torn apart. Another difference between "
"&palapeli; and a real-world jigsaw puzzle is that you cannot combine two "
"pieces that are not true neighbors."
msgstr ""
"Kada ste stavili jedan komad u blizini susjednih komada, oba komada će se "
"automatski spajiti i postaju pridruženi (1). Nakon što su komadi spojeni "
"zajedno, oni ne mogu biti rastrgani. Još jedna razlika između &palapeli; i "
"stvarnog svijeta slagalice je da ne možete kombinirati dva komada koji nisu "
"pravi susjedi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The progress bar below the puzzle table indicates your progress by counting "
"joined pieces (2). &palapeli; will automatically save your progress after "
"every move, so you do not have to worry about saving."
msgstr ""
"Traka napretka ispod tabele slagalice pokazuje vaš napredak brojanjem "
"spojenih komada (2).  palapeli; će automatski spasiti vaš napredak nakon "
"svakog poteza, tako da ne morate brinuti o spašavanju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:210
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can zoom the puzzle table view in or out with the mouse wheel, the "
#| "slider at the bottom right or the buttons at the bottom right (3)."
msgid ""
"You can zoom the puzzle table view in or out with the mouse "
"<mousebutton>wheel</mousebutton>, and at the bottom right (3) with the "
"buttons and the slider."
msgstr ""
"Možete zumirati tabelu slagalice povećevanjem ili smanjivanjem sa kotačem "
"miša, klizačem na dnu desno ili dugmadima na dnu desno (3)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can move the puzzle table view in any direction by clicking and dragging "
"with the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Možete premjestiti pogled tabele slagalice u bilo kojem smjeru klikom i "
"povlačenjem sa &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The movement of the pieces is limited by the <emphasis>puzzle table area</"
"emphasis>. This area is represented on the puzzle table's background by a "
"light rectangular shade. When you move pieces to the border (4) of the "
"puzzle table area, the area will automatically expand to give you more space "
"for moving your puzzle pieces. Near the shaded borders, the mouse cursor "
"changes into a double-headed arrow, indicating that you can adjust the "
"puzzle table area by clicking there and dragging with the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Kretanje komada je ograničena<emphasis>područjem table slagalice</emphasis>. "
"Ovo područje je predstavljeno na pozadini tablice slagalice od pomoću "
"svijetlo osjenčenog kvadrata. Kada premještate komad do okivra (4) tablice  "
"slagalice, područje će se automatski proširiti dajući vam više prostora za "
"premještanje vaših komada slagalice. U blizini osjenčenih okvira, kursor "
"miša se mijenja u dvoglavu strelicu, što znači da možete podesiti područje "
"table slagalice klikom  i povlačenjem sa &LMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:213
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can lock the puzzle table area with the small button (5) to the right "
#| "of the progress bar. The shade (4) around the puzzle table will darken, "
#| "and pieces will now stop moving at the edges of the puzzle table area. It "
#| "is still possible to adjust the size of the puzzle table area manually."
msgid ""
"You can lock the puzzle table area with the small button (5) to the right of "
"the progress bar. The shade (4) around the puzzle table will darken, and "
"pieces will now stop moving at the edges of the puzzle table area. It is "
"still possible to adjust the size of the puzzle table area manually."
msgstr ""
"Možete zaključati područje tablice slagalice sa malim dugmetom (5) na desnoj "
"strani trake napretka. Sjenka (4) oko tablice slagalice će zatamniti, a "
"komadi će se prestati premještati na ivicama područja tablice slagalice. Još "
"uvijek je moguće ručno podesiti veličinu područja tablice slagalice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Preview window"
msgstr "Pregled prozor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Preview is a small window that floats above or to one side of the puzzle "
"table window. It contains an image of the completed puzzle: the picture that "
"would appear on top of the box if this was a real-world jigsaw puzzle."
msgstr ""
"U Preview je mali prozor koji lebdi iznad ili na jednu stranu prozora "
"tablice slagalice. Sadrži sliku završene slagalice: slika koja će se  "
"pojaviti na vrhu kutije ako je ovo bio stvarni svijet jigsaw slagalice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The window can be shown or hidden by using the <guiicon>Preview</guiicon> "
#| "toolbar button or the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem> "
#| "Preview</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. Its size, position and "
#| "visible or not visible setting are saved and restored between runs of "
#| "&palapeli;."
msgid ""
"The window can be shown or hidden by using the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-preview.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> <guiicon>Preview</"
"guiicon> action icon in the toolbar or the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item. Its "
"size, position and visible or not visible setting are saved and restored "
"between runs of &palapeli;."
msgstr ""
"Prozor se može prikazati ili sakriti pomoću tipke <guiicon>Preview</guiicon> "
"toolbar button or the <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guimenuitem> "
"Preview</guimenuitem></menuchoice> stavka izbornika. Njegova veličina, "
"položaj i vidljivost ili nevidljivost postavke su  sačuvane i premještene "
"između staza od  &palapeli;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Being a window, it can be freely moved around the desktop and resized. "
#| "Its Close button will hide it and its Maximize button will expand or "
#| "contract the picture rapidly."
msgid ""
"Being a window, it can be freely moved around the desktop and resized. Its "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton> button will hide it and its "
"<guibutton>Maximize</guibutton> button will expand or contract the picture "
"rapidly."
msgstr ""
"Biti prozor, može se slobodno premještati preko desktopa i mijenjati "
"veličinu. Njegovo dugme Zatvori će sakriti i njegovo dugme Uvećaj će "
"proširiti ili brzo ugovoriti sliku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Preview window has a magnification feature, so it need not take up much "
"space. If you move the mouse over the window, it zooms in quickly to reveal "
"a magnified view of the area under the mouse and the equivalent of a few "
"pieces around it. This is very useful for viewing details of the puzzle and "
"identifying pieces you have found, but it can be tricky to control, "
"especially near the edges of the picture."
msgstr ""
"Prozor Pregled ima funkcije uvećanja, tako da ne mora zauzimati mnogo "
"prostora. Ako se krećete mišem preko prozora, to zumira brzo otkrivanjem "
"uvećanog pogleda na površinu ispod miša i ekvivalenta od nekoliko komada oko "
"njega. Ovo je vrlo korisno za gledanje detalja slagalice i identifikacije "
"komada kog ste pronašli, ali to može biti nezgodno za kontrolu, posebno u "
"blizini ivice slike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mouse interactions"
msgstr "Interakcija  mišem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As described in the previous section, there are plenty of ways to interact "
"with &palapeli;'s puzzle table using the mouse. You can configure freely "
"which actions are triggered by which mouse buttons. (See <link linkend="
"\"configuration-mouseactions\">Game Configuration</link> section for more "
"information on how to configure this.) The following list summarizes all "
"possible mouse actions:"
msgstr ""
"Kao što je opisano u prethodnom poglavlju, postoji mnogo načina da se "
"uzajamno djeluje sa &palapeli; 's tablicom slagalice pomoću miša. Možete "
"slobodno konfigurisatii radnje koje aktiviraju tipke miša. (. "
"Pogledajte<link linkend=\"configuration-mouseactions\">Game Configuration</"
"link> section za više informacija o tome kako ovo konfigurisati) Sljedeći "
"popis rezimira sve moguće radnje miša:"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change size of puzzle table area by dragging its edges"
msgstr "Menjanje veličine površi slagačke table prevlačenjem ivica"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "By default, this action is assigned to the &LMB;."
msgstr "Zadano ova naredba je dodijeljena &LMB;."

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move pieces by dragging"
msgstr "Pomijeranje dijelova prevlačenjem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click and drag a puzzle piece, this piece will be moved. If "
"multiple pieces have been selected and you click and drag one of these "
"pieces, then all pieces are moved. By default, this action is assigned to "
"the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Kada pritisnete i prevučete dio slagalice, dio će biti pomjeren. Ako je "
"odabrano više dijelova a vi pritisnete i prevlačite jedan od njih, svi "
"dijelovi su pomjereni.Zadano, ova naredba je dodijeljena &LMB;."

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move viewport by dragging"
msgstr "Pomjeranje pogleda prevlačenjem"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action moves the view of the entire puzzle table in any direction. By "
"default, it is assigned to the &RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Ova naredba pomijera pogled na cijelu slagalicu u bilo kojem smjeru. Zadano, "
"dodijeljeno je &RMB;."

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:266
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Select several pieces by rubberbanding"
msgid "Select several pieces by rubber banding"
msgstr "Odaberite više dijelova pomoću savijanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click on a free area of the puzzle table instead of a puzzle piece, "
"you can drag a rubberband. When you let the mouse button go, all pieces "
"inside the rubberband are selected. All other pieces are deselected. By "
"default, this action is assigned to the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Kada kliknete na slobodno područje ploče sa slagalicom umjesto dijela "
"slagalice, možete prevući savijeni okvir. Kada pustite tipku miša svi "
"dijelovi unutar savijenog okvira su odabrani. Ostali dijelovi nisu. Zadano, "
"ova naredba je dodijeljena &LMB;."

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select multiple pieces at once"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you click on a puzzle piece, it will be selected or, if it was already "
"selected, it will be deselected. It can also be used to adjust a rubberband "
"selection. By default, this action is assigned to the &LMB; and only "
"available when &Ctrl; is pressed."
msgstr ""
"Kada pritisnete na dio slagalice biće odabran, ili ako je već odabran, "
"odznačavate ga. Može također biti korišteno za prilagođavanje savijenog "
"okvira. Zadano ova naredba je dodijeljena &LMB; i može biti korištena samo "
"kada je &Ctrl; pritisnuto."

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear selections and highlighting"
msgstr "Ukloni izbore i označena područja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on an empty spot in the puzzle table or on a piece that is not already "
"selected."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na prazno mjesto u tabeli slagalice ili na komad koji je već "
"selektovan."

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom the puzzle table view in or out"
msgstr "Povećajte ili smanjite tablicu slagalice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:279
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This action is identical to clicking the buttons either side of the "
#| "slider (3) on the status bar. It is assigned to the mouse wheel by "
#| "default."
msgid ""
"This action is identical to clicking the buttons either side of the slider "
"(3) on the status bar. It is assigned to the mouse <mousebutton>wheel</"
"mousebutton> by default."
msgstr ""
"Ova akcija je identična klik na dugmad s obje strane klizača (3) na "
"statusnoj traci. To je po defaultu dodijeljeno  kotačiću miša."

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to close-up or distant view"
msgstr "Prekidač za pogled iz blizine ili iz daljine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action alternates (toggles) between a close-up and distant view, at the "
"position of the mouse pointer. It is intended mainly to provide fast zooming "
"in large puzzles (300 pieces or more). For more detail, see <link linkend="
"\"large-puzzle-fast-zooming\">Fast zooming between close-up and distant "
"view</link>. By default, the action is assigned to the &MMB;."
msgstr ""
"Ova akcija  se izmjenjuje (mijenja) između pogleda iz blizine i pogleda u "
"daljini, na poziciji pokazivača miša. Namijenjen je prvenstveno da pruži "
"brzo zumiranje u velikim slagalicama (300 komada ili više). Za više detalja, "
"pogledajte see <link linkend=\"large-puzzle-fast-zooming\">Fast zooming "
"between close-up and distant view</link>. Podrazumijevano, akcija je "
"dodijeljena na  &MMB;."

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Teleport pieces to or from a holder"
msgstr "Teleport dio za ili od posjednika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:287
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This action helps you collect, sort and move pieces rapidly in large "
#| "puzzles (300 pieces or more) without dragging and dropping. You can use "
#| "it in smaller puzzles if you wish. For more detail, see <link linkend="
#| "\"large-puzzle-holders\">Using piece-holders</link>. By default, the "
#| "action is assigned to the &LMB; and only available when &Shift; is "
#| "pressed."
msgid ""
"This action helps you collect, sort and move pieces rapidly in large puzzles "
"(300 pieces or more) without dragging and dropping. You can use it in "
"smaller puzzles if you wish. For more detail, see <link linkend=\"large-"
"puzzle-holders\">Using piece-holders</link>. By default, the action is "
"assigned to the &LMB; and only available when &Shift; key is pressed."
msgstr ""
"Ova akcija će Vam pomoći prikupljati, sortirati i brzo pomijerati komade u "
"velikim slagalicama (300 komada ili više), bez povlačenja i ispuštanja. "
"Možete ga koristiti u manjim slagalicama, ako želite. Za više detalja, "
"pogledajte<link linkend=\"large-puzzle-holders\">Using piece-holders</link>. "
"Po zadanom, akciju je dodijeljena na &LMB; i dostupna je samo kada se "
"pritisne &Shift;."

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle lock state of the puzzle table area"
msgstr "Promjena zaključanosti površi slagačke table"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:291
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action is identical to pressing the button (5) on the status bar. By "
"default, this action is not assigned to any mouse button, but you can enable "
"it from <link linkend=\"configuration-mouseactions\">the configuration "
"dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ova akcija je identična pritiskom na dugme (5) na statusnoj traci. Po "
"zadanom, ova akcija nije dodijeljena nijednoj tipki miša, ali možete je "
"omogućiti iz <link linkend=\"configuration-mouseactions\">the configuration "
"dialog</link>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Scroll viewport horizontally</action> and <action>Scroll viewport "
"vertically</action>"
msgstr ""
"<action> Kližite prikaz horizontalno</action> i <action> Kližite prikaz "
"vertikalno </action>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:295
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "By default, this action is not assigned to the mouse wheel, but you can "
#| "enable it from <link linkend=\"configuration-mouseactions\">the "
#| "configuration dialog</link>."
msgid ""
"By default, this action is not assigned to the mouse <mousebutton>wheel</"
"mousebutton>, but you can enable it from <link linkend=\"configuration-"
"mouseactions\">the configuration dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Po zadanom, ova akcija je dodijeljena kotaču miša, a možete je omogućiti iz "
"<link linkend=\"configuration-mouseactions\">the configuration dialog</link>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:304
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Back to collection"
msgid "Back to Collection"
msgstr "Nazad u kolekciju"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305 index.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Go back to the collection to choose another puzzle.</action> Can be "
"used only when you are solving a puzzle."
msgstr ""
"<action>Idite nazad u kolekciju da izaberete drugu slagalicu.</action>Možete "
"koristiti samo kada složite slagalicu ."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle the display of the preview window with the completed puzzle."
msgstr "Promjena ekrana preglednog prozora sa kompletiranom slagalicom."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Facilities for solving large puzzles"
msgstr "Funkcije za rješavanje velikih slagalica"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "General principles"
msgstr "Opšti principi"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&palapeli; can handle large puzzles from 300 to 10,000 pieces, but you need "
"some special facilities to help you work with them on a small screen."
msgstr ""
"&palapeli; može rukovati velikim slagalicama od 300 do 10.000 komada, ali "
"trebate neke posebne funkcije kako bi vam pomogli da radite sa njima na "
"malom ekranu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can create a large puzzle in exactly the same way as a smaller puzzle. "
"See the chapter on <link linkend=\"create-puzzles\">Creating new puzzles</"
"link>, but there are some things you need to think about before you begin. "
"For details see <link linkend=\"large-puzzle-creation\">Creating large "
"puzzles - special concerns</link>."
msgstr ""
"Možete kreirati velike slagalice na isti način kao i manje slagalice. "
"Pogledajte poglavlje o <link linkend=\"create-puzzles\">Creating new "
"puzzles</link>, ali postoje neke stvari o kojima trebate razmišljati prije "
"nego što počnete. Za detalje pogledajte  <link linkend=\"large-puzzle-"
"creation\">Creating large puzzles - special concerns</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The Preview window is very useful in large puzzles: see the section about "
#| "it for a <link linkend=\"puzzletable-preview\"> detailed description</"
#| "link>."
msgid ""
"The Preview window is very useful in large puzzles: see the section about it "
"for a <link linkend=\"puzzletable-preview\">detailed description</link>."
msgstr ""
"Prozor Pregled je veoma koristan u velikima slagalicama: pogledajte odjeljak "
"o tome na  <link linkend=\"puzzletable-preview\"> detailed description</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Managing space and moving around are your next concerns. When you zoom out "
"to view the whole puzzle table, it becomes hard to see individual pieces. If "
"you zoom in and find a piece you are looking for, it is unlikely that the "
"place where it goes will be visible in the view. See the <link linkend="
"\"large-puzzle-space\">Managing space and moving around</link> section for "
"some solutions to these problems and others."
msgstr ""
"Upravljanje prostorom i premještanje je vaša sljedeća briga. Kada umanjite "
"da vidite cijelu tabelu slagalica, postaje teško vidjeti pojedinačni komad. "
"Ako uvećate i pronađete komad koji tražite, malo je vjerojatno da će mjesto "
"koje tražite biti vidljivi u prikazu. Pogledajte <link linkend=\"large-"
"puzzle-space\">Managing space and moving around</link>  odjeljak za nea "
"rješenja za ove probleme i druge."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, you need to collect pieces and convey them to your solution area in "
"some more efficient way than repetitive dragging and dropping over large "
"distances. This is where piece-holders come in."
msgstr ""
"Konačno, morate prikupiti komade i prenijeti ih u svoje područje rješenja na "
"neki efikasniji način nego ponovnim povlačenjem i ispuštanjem na velikim "
"udaljenostima. Ovo je mjesto gdje dolaze posjednici dijelova."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start a large puzzle, you are given a holder (a small floating "
"window) called <quote>Hand</quote> into which you can put pieces when and "
"wherever you see them. Then you can drop them near your solution and work "
"out where each piece has to go. This is like collecting pieces in one hand "
"as you scan a large real-world jigsaw puzzle."
msgstr ""
"Kada pokrenete veliku slagalciu, imate držač (mali plutajući prozor) pod "
"nazivom <quote> Ruka </quote> u koji možete staviti komade  kada i gdje god "
"ih vidite. Tada možete ih ispustiti u blizini vašeg rješenja i odrediti gdje "
"svaki komad mora da ide. Ovo je kao prikupljanje komada u jednoj ruci kao da "
"skenirate veliku jigsaw slagalicu iz stvarnog svijeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:359
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You may need some systematic way to collect and sort pieces by common "
#| "attributes (&eg; edges, sky, skyline, etc.) and so you can use as many "
#| "holders as you like and give them names. Holders are saved continually, "
#| "along with the puzzle table, which means you can use them to build up "
#| "parts of the solution and store them or even to store pieces that you "
#| "wish to put into a <quote>too hard basket</quote> until later. For "
#| "details on how to use holders see the <link linkend=\"large-puzzle-holders"
#| "\">Using piece-holders</link> section."
msgid ""
"You may need some systematic way to collect and sort pieces by common "
"attributes (&eg; edges, sky, skyline, &etc;) and so you can use as many "
"holders as you like and give them names. Holders are saved continually, "
"along with the puzzle table, which means you can use them to build up parts "
"of the solution and store them or even to store pieces that you wish to put "
"into a <quote>too hard basket</quote> until later. For details on how to use "
"holders see the <link linkend=\"large-puzzle-holders\">Using piece-holders</"
"link> section."
msgstr ""
"Možda će vam trebati neki sistematičan način za prikupljanje i sortiranje "
"komada po zajedničkim atributima (&npr; ivicama, nebo, Skyline, itd) i tako "
"da možete koristiti onoliko posjednika koliko želite i dati im imena. "
"Posjednici se kontinualno spašavaju, uz  tablicu slagalice, što znači da ih "
"možete koristiti za izgradnju dijelova rješenja i čuvati ih ili čak za "
"čuvanje komada koji želite staviti u <quote>too hard basket</quote>  dok se "
"ne bude kasno. Za detalje o tome kako koristiti posjednike pogledajte u "
"odjeljku  <quote>too hard basket</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, the <link linkend=\"puzzletable-mouseactions\">Mouse interactions</"
"link> section lists the two special mouse actions that make working with "
"large puzzles quicker and easier: teleporting pieces and zooming to close-up "
"or distant view."
msgstr ""
"Konačno, <link linkend=\"puzzletable-mouseactions\">Mouse interactions</"
"link> odjeljak lista dvije specijalne akcije miša koje čine rad sa velikim "
"slagalicama bržim i lakšim: : teleportacija komada i zumiranje iz blizine "
"ili iz daljine."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating large puzzles - special concerns"
msgstr "Kreiranje velikih slagalica - posebne brige"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Before you create a large puzzle, you should make sure that the image in "
"your source contains enough detail (&ie; enough megapixels). You can use a "
"file utility or photo viewer/editor to find out how many pixels wide and "
"high your picture is when not compressed by JPEG or other image format. As a "
"rough rule of thumb, allow one megapixel per 1,000 pieces. That will give "
"each piece about 1,000 pixels or more than 30 by 30 pixels, making the "
"pieces reasonably sharp at the edges and clear to see when you zoom in. You "
"can work with fewer megapixels, but it may be hard to distinguish and "
"recognize pieces during play."
msgstr ""
"Prije nego što kreirate veliku slagalicu, trebate biti sigurni da je slika u "
"svom izvoru sadrži dovoljno detalja (&tj; dovoljno megapiksela). Možete "
"koristiti datoteku komunalnih ili pregled fotografija / editor da biste "
"saznali koliko je piksela široka i visoka vaša slika kada nije komprimirana "
"u JPEG ili drugi format slike. Kao grubo pravilo, dozvolite  jedan "
"megapiksela na 1000 komada. To će dati svakom komadu oko 1.000 piksela ili "
"više od 30 do 30 piksela, čineći komad razumno oštrim na ivicama i jasno "
"vidljivim kada ga uvećate. Možete raditi s manje megapiksela, ali može biti "
"teško razlikovati i prepoznati komade tokom reprodukcije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you create or restart a large puzzle, it may be best to avoid using the "
"bevel and shadowing features of &palapeli; (see the <link linkend="
"\"configuration-general\">General settings</link> section), because they "
"make loading slower and highlighting harder to see when the pieces in the "
"view are very small. More prominent highlighting appears when shadowing is "
"not used."
msgstr ""
"Kada kreirate ili ponovo pokrenete veliku slagalicu, može biti najbolje da "
"to izbjegnete pomoću bevel i shadowing karakteristike &palapeli; (vidi <link "
"linkend=\"configuration-general\">General settings</link> odjeljak), jer oni "
"čine učitavanje sporijim i naglašavanje težim  da bi vidjeli kada su komadi "
"u prikazu vrlo mali. Više istaknuto naglašavane pojavljuje se kada se ne "
"koristi shadowing."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Managing space and moving around"
msgstr "Upravljanje prostorom i kretanje po njemu"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:408
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allocating space on the puzzle table"
msgstr "Dodjeljeni prostor na tablice slagalice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:409
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you create or restart a puzzle, the pieces are shuffled and placed "
#| "randomly into grid locations on the puzzle table. Two settings affect the "
#| "space required, see <link linkend=\"configuration\">Game Configuration</"
#| "link> for a list of settings provided via <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &palapeli;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> "
#| "or, on Apple OS X, <menuchoice><guimenu>&palapeli;</guimenu> "
#| "<guimenuitem>Preferences...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"When you create or restart a puzzle, the pieces are shuffled and placed "
"randomly into grid locations on the puzzle table. Two settings affect the "
"space required, see <link linkend=\"configuration\">Game Configuration</"
"link> for a list of settings provided via <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &palapeli;…</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or, "
"on &macOS;, <menuchoice><guimenu>&palapeli;</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preferences…</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Kada kreirate ili restartujete slagalicu, komadi se miješaju i postavljaju "
"slučajnim odabirom u mrežu lokacija na tablici slagalice. Dvije postavke "
"utiču  na potrebni prostor, pogledajte  <link linkend=\"configuration"
"\">Konfiguracija igre</link> za listu odobrenih postavki od  "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriši "
"&palapeli;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>  ili, na Apple OS X, "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>&palapeli;</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Postavke...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:422
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The spacing of pieces in puzzle grids can be set from 1.0 to 1.5 times "
#| "the height and width of the highest and widest pieces. Smaller settings "
#| "pack the pieces into the view better, but larger ones allow more space "
#| "for dragging, dropping and rubberbanding. The default is 1.3, but 1.1 is "
#| "very workable in large puzzles. The setting applies to puzzles of all "
#| "sizes, and also affects grids used with piece-holders (see <link linkend="
#| "\"large-puzzle-holders\">Using piece-holders</link>) or when re-arranging "
#| "pieces automatically on the puzzle table, using "
#| "<menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Rearrange pieces</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"The spacing of pieces in puzzle grids can be set from 1.0 to 1.5 times the "
"height and width of the highest and widest pieces. Smaller settings pack the "
"pieces into the view better, but larger ones allow more space for dragging, "
"dropping and rubber banding. The default is 1.3, but 1.1 is very workable in "
"large puzzles. The setting applies to puzzles of all sizes, and also affects "
"grids used with piece-holders (see <link linkend=\"large-puzzle-holders"
"\">Using piece-holders</link>) or when re-arranging pieces automatically on "
"the puzzle table, using the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem>Rearrange Pieces</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Razmak između komada u mrežama slagalice može se postaviti od 1,0 do 1,5 "
"puta visine i širine najvišeg i najšireg komada. Manje postavke pakuju "
"komade u bolji prikaz, ali one veće omogućavaju više prostora za povlačenje, "
"puštanje i rubberbanding. Standardno je 1,3, ali 1,1 je vrlo izvodljiv u "
"velikim slagalicama. Postavka se odnosi na slagalice svih veličina, a "
"također utječe na mreže korištene  s komadom-posjednikom (pogledajte <link "
"linkend=\"large-puzzle-holders\">Using piece-holders</link>) ili kada ponovo "
"uređujete komade automatski na tablici slagalice, koristeći "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Rearrange pieces</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:438
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The other setting provides space on the puzzle table of exactly the right "
#| "size for building your solution. The default is for it to appear in the "
#| "center, with the pieces distributed evenly around the outside. On "
#| "average, this should put the pieces closest to where they have to go "
#| "eventually. You can also choose to use any of the four corners or have no "
#| "space (option None), in which case you have to clear space manually, "
#| "perhaps by expanding the puzzle table area (see <link linkend="
#| "\"puzzletable-moves\">Basic moves</link>). The solution space setting "
#| "affects puzzles down to 20 pieces, but with fewer than 20 pieces solution "
#| "spaces are pointless."
msgid ""
"The other setting provides space on the puzzle table of exactly the right "
"size for building your solution. The default is for it to appear in the "
"center, with the pieces distributed evenly around the outside. On average, "
"this should put the pieces closest to where they have to go eventually. You "
"can also choose to use any of the four corners or have no space (option "
"<guilabel>None</guilabel>), in which case you have to clear space manually, "
"perhaps by expanding the puzzle table area (see <link linkend=\"puzzletable-"
"moves\">Basic moves</link>). The solution space setting affects puzzles down "
"to 20 pieces, but with fewer than 20 pieces solution spaces are pointless."
msgstr ""
"Druga postavka osigurava prostor na tabeli slagalice baš prave veličine za "
"izgradnju vašeg rješenja. Standardno za to je da se pojavi u centru, sa "
"komadima ravnomjerno raspoređenim oko spoljašnosti. U prosjeku, ov bi "
"trebalo staviti komada najbliže gdje moraju da idu na kraju. Također možete "
"odabrati da koriste bilo koji od četiri ugla, ili  nemati prostora (opcija "
"None), u tom slučaju morate ručno očistiti prostor, možda proširenjem "
"područja tablice slagalice (pogledajte see <link linkend=\"puzzletable-moves"
"\">Basic moves</link>). Postavka rješenja prostora isplati se za slagalice "
"do 20 komada, ali sa manje od 20 komada rješenja prostora su besmislena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:454
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "As the puzzle solution progresses, pieces move into the solution area and "
#| "leave spaces elsewhere. It may be helpful to pack the remaining pieces "
#| "closer together. If so, select some pieces using rubberbanding or &Ctrl; "
#| "and &LMB;, then use <menuchoice><shortcut> <keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> "
#| "<guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rearrange pieces</guimenuitem></"
#| "menuchoice> or simply the shortcut key (default <keycap>R</keycap>). The "
#| "pieces are packed into a grid and remain selected, so that they can be "
#| "easily moved to a better position, if required. This is also a way to "
#| "gather together pieces with some common attribute, but using piece-"
#| "holders is more powerful."
msgid ""
"As the puzzle solution progresses, pieces move into the solution area and "
"leave spaces elsewhere. It may be helpful to pack the remaining pieces "
"closer together. If so, select some pieces using rubber banding or hold the "
"&Ctrl; key and click with the &LMB;, then use the "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Rearrange Pieces</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item or simply "
"the shortcut (default is the <keycap>R</keycap> key). The pieces are packed "
"into a grid and remain selected, so that they can be easily moved to a "
"better position, if required. This is also a way to gather together pieces "
"with some common attribute, but using piece-holders is more powerful."
msgstr ""
"Kako rješenje slagalice napreduje, komadi se premještaju u području rješenja "
"i ostavljaju prostor drugdje. To može biti od pomoći za pakovanje preostalih "
"komada bliže jedno drugima. Ako je tako, odaberite neke komade pomoću "
"rubberbanding ili &Ctrl; i &LMB;, zatim koristite <menuchoice><shortcut> "
"<keycap>R</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ponovo  "
"složi dijelove</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ili jednostavno taster prečicu "
"(default <keycap> R </keycap>). Komadi su upakovani u mrežu i ostaju "
"odabrani, tako da se oni mogu lahko premjestiti u bolji položaj, ako je to "
"potrebno. To je također način da se okupe zajedno komadi sa nekim "
"zajedničkim atributom, ali koristeći komad-posjednik je moćniji."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fast zooming between close-up and distant view"
msgstr "Brzo zumiranje izmađu pogleda iz blizine ili pogleda iz daljine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a puzzle is loaded, &palapeli; calculates distant and close-up views "
"and displays the distant view, which shows the entire puzzle table area. The "
"close-up view shows pieces at a convenient viewing size for your eyes and "
"your screen and desktop. Use the &MMB; to switch quickly between the two "
"views, at a location where the mouse is pointing. Then you can home in "
"quickly on any piece in the puzzle table and see what shape it is and what "
"part of the picture it contains."
msgstr ""
"Kada je slagalica učitana, &palapeli; izračunava  pogled iz blizine i pogled "
"iz daljine i prikazuje se pogled iz daljine, koji pokazuje cijelo područje "
"tablice slagalice. Pogled izbliza pokazuje komad na pogodne veličine  za "
"vaše oči i vaš ekran i desktop. Koristite &MMB; za brzo prebacivanje između "
"dva pogleda, na mjestu gdje miš pokazuje. Onda možete brzo postaviti bilo "
"koji komad u tablici slagalice i vidjeti koji je to oblik i ono što dio "
"slike sadrži."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can adjust the scale of either view by zooming manually and your setting "
"will be remembered next time you switch the view by using the &MMB;. Puzzles "
"of all sizes have the fast zooming feature, but in puzzles with less than "
"100 pieces the two views are almost the same as each other. In other words, "
"the pieces are easy to see when you view the whole puzzle table."
msgstr ""
"Možete podesiti skalu bilo kojeg pogleda zumiranjem ručno i postavke će se "
"pamtiti sljedeći putkada  uključite prikaz pomoću &MMB;. Slagalice svih "
"veličina imaju funkciju brzog zumiranja, ali u slagalicama s manje od 100 "
"komada dva pogleda su gotovo ista. Drugim riječima, komadi su lahko vidljivi "
"kada pogledate cijelu tablicu slagalice."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Moving around in a large puzzle"
msgstr "Premještanje u velikim slagalicama"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The hard way to move pieces in a large puzzle is to select them and then "
"alternately drag the pieces and the puzzle table (&LMB; and &RMB;) until you "
"get to your destination. A much easier way to do the same thing is to select "
"the pieces, zoom to distant view (&MMB;, see above), drag the pieces to the "
"destination in one move (&LMB;) and then zoom to close-up view (&MMB;). This "
"is also a good way to retrieve a single stray piece, but dragging that tiny "
"piece across the puzzle table, without losing the selection, can be tricky "
"if there are thousands of pieces."
msgstr ""
"Teži način da se premještaju komadi u velikim slagalicama je da ih "
"izaberete, a zatim naizmjenično povlačite komade i tablicu slagalice (&LMB; "
"i &RMB;) dok ne dođete do svog odredišta. A mnogo lakši način da uradite "
"istu stvar je da odaberete komad, zumirati na pogled iz daljine (&MMB;, vidi "
"gore), povučete komad do odredišta u jednom potezu (&LMB;), a zatim zumirate "
"na pogled izbliza (&MMB;). Ovo je također dobar način da preuzmete jedan "
"zalutali komad, ali povlačenjem tog malog komada slagalice preko tablice, "
"bez gubitka izbora, može biti nezgodno ako hiljade komada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:511
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another way to navigate and search the puzzle table systematically is to "
"zoom in on the top left corner (&MMB;), then use the empty spaces in the "
"scroll bars to step through the table horizontally or vertically, one fixed-"
"size <quote>page</quote> at a time. This technique is very effective when "
"you are using piece-holders to collect pieces you are looking for. If you "
"keep the close-up scale fixed and always start at the same place, you will "
"always get <quote>pages</quote> of fixed size and contents."
msgstr ""
"Drugi način za navigaciju i pretraživanje tablice slagalice sistematski je  "
"uvećavanje u gornjem lijevom uglu (&MMB;), a zatim korištenje praznog "
"prostora u kliznoj traci na korak do tablice horizontalno ili vertikalno, "
"jedna fiksna veličina <quote>page</quote>  odjednom. Ova tehnika je vrlo "
"efikasna kada se koristi komad-posjednik za prikupljanje komada kojeg "
"tražite. Ako držite izbliza skalu fiksnom i uvijek pokrećete na istom "
"mjestu, uvijek ćete dobiti <quote>pages</quote>  ili  fiksne veličine i "
"sadržaje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:525
#, no-c-format
msgid "Visibility of pieces in large puzzles"
msgstr "Vidljivost dijelova u velikim slagalicama"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:526
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In large jigsaw puzzles on a small screen it can be hard to see what you are "
"doing. For example, with a 10,000 piece puzzle on a 1440 by 900 screen, the "
"pieces in the distant view of the puzzle table are about 7 pixels across. At "
"this scale, it is hard to see picture, color, piece-shape or even "
"highlighting."
msgstr ""
"U velikim jigsaw slagalicama na malom ekranu može biti teško vidjeti šta "
"radite. Na primjer, sa 10,000 dijelova slagalice na 1440 od 900 ekrana, "
"dijelovi u pogledu iz daljine tablice slagalice su preko oko 7 pixela. Po "
"ovoj skali, teško je vidjeti sliku, boju, oblik dijela ili čak podvlačenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&palapeli; has always had a choice of backgrounds and background colors and "
"that helps visibility. Added to these is a more prominent highlighting "
"scheme, which appears if you do not choose shadowing, and a setting to "
"choose the color of the highlight, to contrast with the background and most "
"pieces. Also these settings are now saved and restored with each puzzle. So "
"each puzzle can have the background and highlighting that best suits its "
"overall picture. It is worth experimenting with settings when you create a "
"large puzzle, but you may need to reload or restart the puzzle before all "
"changes can take effect."
msgstr ""
"&palapeli; uvijek imaju izbor podloge i boje podloge i to pomaže "
"vidljivosti. Dodavanje u ovo je više istaknuto podvlačenjem šeme, koja se "
"pojavljuje ako niste izabrali sjenčenje, i postavke za odabir boje i "
"podvlačenje, da se suprostave sa podlogom i većinom dijelova. Također ove "
"postavke su sada sačuvane i premještene sa svakom slagalicom. Dakle svaka "
"slagalica može imati podlogu i podvlačenje koje najbolje odgovara njenoj "
"slici. Gore je eksperimentisati sa postavkama kada kreirate veliku "
"slagalicu, ali trebate ponovo učitati i ponovo pokrenuti slagalicu prije "
"nego promjene krenu djelovati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using piece-holders"
msgstr "Korištenje komada posjednika"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "What are piece-holders?"
msgstr "Šta su komadi posjednici?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Piece-holders are perhaps the most useful feature of &palapeli; for helping "
"solve large puzzles. They are small, floating windows into which you can "
"sort groups of pieces, such as <quote>edges</quote>, <quote>sky</quote>, "
"<quote>skyline</quote> or <quote>white house on left</quote>. Initially they "
"appear at a minimum size which is just large enough to show four pieces at "
"close-up scale, so they are quite easy to fit in next to the main puzzle "
"table window."
msgstr ""
"Komadi posjednici su možda najviše korištene funkcije &palapeli; za "
"pomaganje rješavanja velikih slagalica. Oni su mali, plutajući prozori u "
"koje možete sortirati grupe dijelova, kao  <quote>edges</quote>, <quote>sky</"
"quote>, <quote>skyline</quote>  ili <quote>white house on left</quote>. U "
"početku, oni se postave na minimalnu veličinu koja je dovoljna velikim za "
"prikaz četiri dijelana izbliza skali, tako da ih je lahko sljedeće staviti u "
"prozor glavne slagalice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:567
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Being windows, holders can be freely moved around the desktop and "
#| "resized. The Close button will delete the holder, but only if it contains "
#| "no pieces. The Maximize button will expand or contract the holder "
#| "rapidly. The holder can contain any number of pieces (maybe hundreds). A "
#| "Maximize action can be useful when reviewing the contents or constructing "
#| "a sub-assembly inside the holder."
msgid ""
"Being windows, holders can be freely moved around the desktop and resized. "
"The <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button will delete the holder, but only if "
"it contains no pieces. The <guibutton>Maximize</guibutton> button will "
"expand or contract the holder rapidly. The holder can contain any number of "
"pieces (maybe hundreds). A maximize action can be useful when reviewing the "
"contents or constructing a sub-assembly inside the holder."
msgstr ""
"U postojećim prozorima, posjednici  se mogu  slobodno kretati oko desktopa i "
"mijenjati veličinu. Dugme Zatvori će izbrisati posjednika, ali samo ako on "
"ne sadrži komad. Dugme Uvećaj će proširiti ili brzo ugovoriti posjednika. "
"Posjednik može sadržavati bilo koji broj komada (možda stotine).Uvećaj "
"akcije mogu biti korisne pri razmatranju sadržaja ili izgradnje podsklopa "
"unutar posjednika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can have as many holders as you like. There is usually one which is "
"active - outlined in blue. It is the target for actions such as transferring "
"pieces or deleting a holder."
msgstr ""
"Možete imati koliko želite posjednika. Obično je jedan koji je aktivan - "
"plavom bojom podvučen. On je meta za akcije kao prenošenje dijelova ili "
"brisanje posjednika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating and deleting holders"
msgstr "Kreiranje i brisanje posjednika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start a large puzzle, a holder called <quote>Hand</quote> is "
"created automatically. This may be the only holder you need with puzzles of "
"300 to 750 pieces, but you can have as many holders as you like, even with "
"puzzles of less than 300 pieces."
msgstr ""
"Kada pokrenete veliku slagalicu, posjednik nazvan <quote>Hand</quote>  je "
"kreiran automatski. Ovo može biti samo posjednik kojeg trebate sa "
"slagalicama od 300 do 750 komada, ali možete imati kao manjem posjednika "
"ukoliko želite, čak sa slagalicama sa manje od 300 komada."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:591
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To create or delete a holder, use <menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>C</"
#| "keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem> Create piece "
#| "holder...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>D</"
#| "keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem> Delete piece "
#| "holder</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, or simply the shortcut keys <keycap>C</"
#| "keycap> and <keycap>D</keycap>, or the Close button to delete. When you "
#| "create a holder, you are asked to give it a name, but that is not "
#| "essential. Usually the holder is at close-up scale and you can easily see "
#| "what kind of piece is in it."
msgid ""
"To create or delete a holder, use the <menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>C</"
"keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem> Create Piece Holder…"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or <menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>D</keycap></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Move</guimenu><guimenuitem> Delete Piece Holder</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu items, or simply the <keycap>C</keycap> and "
"<keycap>D</keycap> keys, or the <guibutton>Close</guibutton> button to "
"delete. When you create a holder, you are asked to give it a name, but that "
"is not essential. Usually the holder is at close-up scale and you can easily "
"see what kind of piece is in it."
msgstr ""
"Da izbrišete ili kreirate posjednika, koristite "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>C</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem> Create piece holder...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycap>D</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Move</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem> Delete piece holder</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, ili "
"jednostavno kratice <keycap>C</keycap> i <keycap>D</keycap>, ili Zatvori "
"dugme da izbrišete. Kada kreirate posjednika, pitat će vas da mu date ime, "
"ali to nije esencijalno. Obično je posjednik na izbliza skali i možete lahko "
"vidjeti koja vrsta komada je u njemu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you delete a holder, it must be active (outlined in blue) and empty of "
"pieces. If the holder to be deleted is not active, click on it. After "
"deletion, there is no active holder, so click on one of those that are left."
msgstr ""
"Kada izbrišete posjednika, on mora biti aktivan (podvučenom plavom) i "
"praznih komada. Ako je posjednik kojeg brišete neaktivan, kliknite na njega. "
"Nakon brisanja, nema aktivnog posjednika, pa kliknite na jednog od ovih koji "
"su preostali."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid "Transferring pieces into and out of holders"
msgstr "Prenos dijelova u i iz posjednika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:614
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Transferring pieces by dragging and dropping is not possible with "
#| "holders, nor is it needed. Instead, you can transfer pieces instantly by "
#| "<quote>teleporting</quote>, as in <quote>Star Trek</quote>. Teleporting "
#| "works by using the &Shift; and &LMB; together."
msgid ""
"Transferring pieces by dragging and dropping is not possible with holders, "
"nor is it needed. Instead, you can transfer pieces instantly by "
"<quote>teleporting</quote>, as in <quote>Star Trek</quote>. Teleporting "
"works by hold the &Shift; key and click with the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Prenos komada povlačenjem i puštanjem nije moguće sa posjednicima, ili nije "
"potrebno. Umjesto toga, možete prenosti dijelove odmah <quote>teleporting</"
"quote>, kao u <quote>Star Trek</quote>. Teleportacija radi korištenjem "
"&Shift; i &LMB; zajedno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:620
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To transfer pieces to a holder, make sure your target holder is active "
#| "(outlined in blue), then select some pieces on the puzzle table and click "
#| "with &Shift; and &LMB;. Or you can just click on one piece at a time with "
#| "&Shift; and &LMB;. The transferred pieces vanish from the puzzle table "
#| "and reappear, highlighted, in the holder. As they arrive, they are "
#| "automatically packed into a grid and the last piece transferred is "
#| "centered in the view."
msgid ""
"To transfer pieces to a holder, make sure your target holder is active "
"(outlined in blue), then select some pieces on the puzzle table and hold the "
"&Shift; key and click with the &LMB;. Or you can just click on one piece at "
"a time by hold the &Shift; key and click with the &LMB;. The transferred "
"pieces vanish from the puzzle table and reappear, highlighted, in the "
"holder. As they arrive, they are automatically packed into a grid and the "
"last piece transferred is centered in the view."
msgstr ""
"Za prenos komada posjedniku, budite sigurni da je vaš zadani posjednik "
"aktivan (podvučen plavom), zatim selektujte neki komad na tablici slagalice "
"i kliknite sa &Shift; i &LMB;. Ili možte samo kliknuti na jedan komad "
"istovremeno sa &Shift; i &LMB;. Prenešeni komadi nestaju iz tablice "
"slagalice i ponovo nastaju, naglašeni, u posjedniku. Kada stignu, oni su "
"automatski upakovani  mrežu i posljednji prenešeni komad je centriran u "
"pogedu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:631
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To transfer pieces out of a holder, select a piece or pieces inside the "
#| "holder, then return to the puzzle table and click on an empty spot where "
#| "you would like the piece(s) to appear, using &Shift; and &LMB;. Avoid "
#| "clicking on a piece that is already on the puzzle table: it will send the "
#| "piece to the holder - not what you want. If you accidentally do this with "
#| "a large joined-up piece (&ie; part of your solution), there is a warning "
#| "message and an opportunity to cancel."
msgid ""
"To transfer pieces out of a holder, select a piece or pieces inside the "
"holder, then return to the puzzle table and click on an empty spot where you "
"would like the piece(s) to appear, hold the &Shift; key and click with the "
"&LMB;. Avoid clicking on a piece that is already on the puzzle table: it "
"will send the piece to the holder - not what you want. If you accidentally "
"do this with a large joined-up piece (&ie; part of your solution), there is "
"a warning message and an opportunity to cancel."
msgstr ""
"Za prenos komada iz posjednika, selektujte komad ili komade u posjedniku, "
"zatim se vratite na tablicu slagalice i klknite na prazno mjesto gdje želite "
"da se pojavi komad(i), korištenjem &Shift; i &LMB;. Izbjegavanjem klikanja "
"na komad koji je već u tabeli slagalice: poslat će komad hoderu - nije ono "
"što želite. Ako ste slučajno uradili ovo sa velikim pridruženim komadom "
"(&npr; dio vašeg rješenja), pojavit će se poruka upozorenja i mogućnost da "
"otkažete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pieces stay highlighted after teleporting. That allows you to reverse the "
"action quickly if you accidentally transfer the wrong pieces or use the "
"wrong holder. Also, on the puzzle table, you can easily adjust the position "
"of a piece or pieces that have just arrived or move a piece into the "
"solution."
msgstr ""
"Komadi ostaju naglašeni nakon teleportacije. To vam dozvoljava da "
"preokrenete brzo akciju ako ste slučajno premjestili pogrešan komad ili "
"koristili pogrešnog posjednika. Takođe, na tabeli slagalice, možete lahko "
"podesiti poziciju komada ili komada koji su tek stigli ili premjestiti komad "
"u rješenje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:651
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Teleporting also works between holders. Start as if you are going to "
#| "transfer pieces to the puzzle table, but then use &Shift; and &LMB; in an "
#| "empty spot in another holder. To reverse the process, go back to the "
#| "original holder and click with &Shift; and &LMB; again."
msgid ""
"Teleporting also works between holders. Start as if you are going to "
"transfer pieces to the puzzle table, but then by hold the &Shift; key and "
"click with the &LMB; in an empty spot in another holder. To reverse the "
"process, go back to the original holder and hold the &Shift; key and click "
"with the &LMB; again."
msgstr ""
"Teleportacija takođe radi između posjednika. Pokrenete je ako želite "
"prenijeti komad u tabelu slagalice, ali onda koristite &Shift; i &LMB; na "
"prazno mjesto u drugom posjedniku. Da preokrenete proces, idite nazad u "
"originalni posjednik i klknite sa &SHIFT; I &LMB; ponovo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorting pieces"
msgstr "Sortiranje komada"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To sort pieces into holders efficiently as you search through a large "
"puzzle, use the technique for stepping through the puzzle a <quote>page</"
"quote> at a time, <link linkend=\"large-puzzle-navigating\"> as described "
"earlier</link>, combined with holders and teleporting to collect pieces as "
"you go. When you have scanned the whole puzzle table, zoom to a close-up of "
"your solution area and place the pieces you have collected. Or you can pre-"
"assemble pieces in holders."
msgstr ""
"Da efikasno sortirate komade u posjedniku pretragom kroz veliku slagalicu, "
"koristite tehniku korak po korak kroz slagalicu a <quote>page</quote>  na "
"vrijeme, <link linkend=\"large-puzzle-navigating\"> kao što je opisano "
"ranije </link>, kombinovanjem sa posjednikom i prenosom za sakupljanje "
"komada kao što ide. Kada imate skeniranu cijelu tabelu slagalice, zumirajte "
"za pogled izbliza vašeg područja rješenja i mjesto komada kojeg sakupljate. "
"Ili možete premontirati komade u posjednicima."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:676
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other holder actions"
msgstr "Druge akcije posjednika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:677
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Piece-holders support all the functions of the puzzle table (see <link "
#| "linkend=\"puzzletable-moves\">Basic moves</link>), except that you can "
#| "only zoom by using the scroll-wheel or the &MMB;."
msgid ""
"Piece-holders support all the functions of the puzzle table (see <link "
"linkend=\"puzzletable-moves\">Basic moves</link>), except that you can only "
"zoom by using the scroll-<mousebutton>wheel</mousebutton> or the &MMB;."
msgstr ""
"Komad posjednik podržava sve funkcije tabele slagalice ( pogledajte <link "
"linkend=\"puzzletable-moves\">Osnovni pokreti</link>), osim ako možete samo "
"zumirati pomjeranja koluta na mišu ili &MMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:682
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
